statements: SELECT * FROM user_interaction_data ORDER BY interaction_time DESC;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interaction_data WHERE user_id = 10;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, interaction_data FROM user_interaction_data WHERE interaction_type = 'click' ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id FROM user_interaction_data;
SELECT interaction_type, COUNT(*) as total_interactions FROM user_interaction_data GROUP BY interaction_type ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_interaction_data WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY interaction_time DESC;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, interaction_data FROM user_interaction_data WHERE user_id = 2 AND interaction_type = 'click';
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, interaction_time FROM user_interaction_data WHERE interaction_type LIKE '%hover%' ORDER BY interaction_time ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id FROM user_interaction_data WHERE interaction_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM user_interaction_data GROUP BY user_id, interaction_type ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_interactions;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interactions ORDER BY interaction_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interactions WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, MAX(quiz_attempts) FROM learning_progress GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM user_interactions GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, interaction_timestamp FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_type='click' ORDER BY interaction_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM learning_progress WHERE user_id=100 AND quiz_attempts >= 3;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(interaction_type) AS total_interactions FROM user_interactions GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_interactions > 5 ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, DATE_FORMAT(interaction_timestamp, '%Y-%m-%d') AS interaction_date FROM user_interactions WHERE user_id=200 ORDER BY interaction_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT LP.user_id, SUM(LP.module_completed) AS total_modules_completed, COUNT(UI.interaction_type) AS total_interactions FROM learning_progress LP LEFT JOIN user_interactions UI ON LP.user_id=UI.user_id GROUP BY LP.user_id HAVING total_modules_completed > 10 AND total_interactions > 20;

SELECT user_id, MAX(progress_percentage) AS highest_progress FROM user_progress GROUP BY user_id HAVING highest_progress > 50
SELECT DISTINCT interaction_type FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_timestamp >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY interaction_type
SELECT user_id, COUNT(feedback_id) AS feedback_count FROM user_feedback GROUP BY user_id HAVING feedback_count > 0 ORDER BY feedback_count DESC

SELECT course_id, COUNT(*) FROM course_activities GROUP BY course_id;

SELECT user_id, action_type, timestamp FROM user_actions WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT user_id, MAX(timestamp) AS latest_action FROM user_actions GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY latest_action DESC LIMIT 5;
